rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I think us Phonexes in Superbia are
getting thinner.

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
There's barely enough grass and bugs
to subsist on around here, after all...

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But still, we all fight to survive
somehow. We're stronger than
we look!

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Huh? We look more or less the same
as other Phonexes to you?

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I won't believe it! My stomach
is always growling away like an
angry Armu!
